reviewText: My 4 yr old granddaughter loves this DVD.  One adverture had her counting up to 100, another finding lost animals representing letters in the alphabet.  It was more than just a passive learning experience.

reviewText: My two year old Grand daughter loves this Dora and just loved this video. I didn't order it in time for Christmas but was very pleased that I did receive it in a very timely manner. When I received this video I was pleased that it was just as it was described. It was in great condition and worked well. We are still enjoying this video.
